titles.title: Expressing the profound sorrow of the House of Representatives on the death of the Honorable James L. Hagedorn.
Expressing the profound sorrow of the House of Representatives on the death of the Honorable James L. Hagedorn.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: This resolution honors the life of James Hagedorn, former Representative of Minnesota, and offers the condolence of the House of Representatives regarding his death.
